1.  THis Code is a Windows Phone Apps Crawler which collects apps from Window Phone Marketplace (US).
2.  It utilizes HttpClient library to retrieve webpages and utilizes HtmlParser to parse useful information.
3.  There are two seperate crawlers. One is used to collected app information, such as app id, name, description, developer, rating,
download number. The other is used to collect apps' comments from users.
